Submit when you have a high-value item (25-35 points) and no safe actions left.

message: Focus on growing individual ingredients with the growth serum first. Then, combine two 'grown small' items, preferably with different habitat features (e.g., lives in air + lives in water/land). Once you have a combined small item, repeatedly use the growth serum on it. It seems to reach maximum value (around 30-35) at the 'ultra-grown' stage. Avoid using the mutation catalyst on any combined items, as it consistently led to drastic value drops in my experience. Also, avoid applying the growth serum to combined large animals after their initial combination, as this also reduced their value.
